    {
      "id": "b3-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80, "y": 866,
      "width": 360, "height": 36,
      "text": "Design for failure first, features second.",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#f38ba8", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "seed": 1033, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1033,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Design for failure first, features second.", "angle": 0, "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "b3-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80, "y": 916,
      "width": 360, "height": 148,
      "text": "Developers design the happy path.\n\nArchitects design for the crash, the timeout,\nthe retry storm, and the cascade failure.\n\nThe question isn't \"will it work?\"\nIt's \"what happens when it doesn't?\"",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#a6adc8", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "seed": 1034, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1034,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Developers design the happy path.\n\nArchitects design for the crash, the timeout,\nthe retry storm, and the cascade failure.\n\nThe question isn't \"will it work?\"\nIt's \"what happens when it doesn't?\"", "angle": 0, "groupIds": []
    },

