    },
    {
      "id": "b7-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80, "y": 2226,
      "width": 360, "height": 36,
      "text": "Draw the failure boundary before the system.",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#f5c2e7", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "seed": 1073, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1073,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Draw the failure boundary before the system.", "angle": 0, "groupIds": []
    },
    {
      "id": "b7-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80, "y": 2276,
      "width": 360, "height": 148,
      "text": "\"If this service fails, what else fails with it?\"\n\nThe blast radius determines your SLA,\nyour on-call load, and your recovery strategy.\n\nIsolate failure domains first.\nBuild features inside them second.",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#a6adc8", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "seed": 1074, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1074,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"If this service fails, what else fails with it?\"\n\nThe blast radius determines your SLA,\nyour on-call load, and your recovery strategy.\n\nIsolate failure domains first.\nBuild features inside them second.", "angle": 0, "groupIds": []
    },

